00:17:46,804 --> 00:17:47,945
Same thing, just written twice.

348
00:17:48,025 --> 00:17:50,167
On the left, I would express it as each frame,

349
00:17:50,207 --> 00:17:53,190
we take a 90-10 blend of ourselves

